    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade 2008 Honda S2000 CR represents the pinnacle of the AP2 chassis. Featuring the high-revving F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC inline-four paired with a precise, close-ratio six-speed manual gearbox, this example delivers an unfiltered analog driving experience. The factory-tuned suspension utilizes increased spring rates and stiffer anti-roll bars, complemented by the CR-exclusive aerodynamic package which significantly reduces lift at high velocities. Mechanically flawless, the Torsen helical limited-slip differential provides exceptional corner-exit traction, while the engine maintains optimal compression across all cylinders. Every original VIN tag is present, and the undercarriage remains in concours condition. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a legendary roadster in its most focused, track-oriented execution.",
      "price": 48500.0,
